        <p>Calibrate the extruder steps/mm:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Measure 100mm of filament</li>
            <li>Run 100mm extrusion command</li>
            <li>Calculate actual movement and adjust E-step value</li>
        </ol>
        <h3>3. Nozzle Height Adjustment</h3>
        <p>Ensure proper first layer height:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Set nozzle at 0.1mm above bed</li>
            <li>Use a business card to check consistency</li>
            <li>Verify with test prints</li>
        </ul>
